These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-1::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: ebony, black, lavender, brown
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, aristoff, old-henry, chaman
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, coffee, hot-chocolate, cola
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: january, october, december, february
1. the aristoff-smoker is the person who likes ebony##1
2. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the game-smoker##1
4. the person who likes brown is on the right of the aristoff-smoker##1
5. the old-henry-smoker is on the right of the person who likes black##1
6. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
7. the aristoff-smoker is the person who's birthday is in january##1
8. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1
9. the person who likes brown is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Color         | ebony  | brown  | black | lavender |
| Cigar           | aristoff | game | chaman  | old-henry  |
| Beverage   | cola       | hot-chocolate      | 7up | coffee      |
| Birthday           | january          | october     | december    | february     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-2::.
House: art-deco, victorian, townhouse, cottage
The people have 4 different jobs:  paramedic, designer, photographer, manager
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: davidoff, game, aristoff, montecristo
There are 4 different nationalities: nigerian, italian, indonesian, german
1. the paramedic is on the far right##1
2. the montecristo-smoker is the nigerian##1
3. the photographer is on the right of the art-deco house##1
4. the indonesian is on the left of the designer##1
5. the montecristo-smoker is on the left of the davidoff-smoker##1
6. the townhouse house is the aristoff-smoker##1
7. the game-smoker is on the left of the victorian house##1
8. the indonesian is on the left of the art-deco house##1
9. the nigerian is on the right of the german##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| House      | townhouse     | art-deco       | victorian | cottage        |
| Job          | manager     | designer       | photographer   | paramedic   |
| Cigar   | aristoff      | game       | montecristo     | davidoff    |
| Nationality         | indonesian | german | nigerian | italian |

