.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-3::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: grey, amber, lavender, ivory
The people have 4 different hobbies: woodworking, singing, collecting, sudoku
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, davidoff, game, oliveros
4 different games are played: backgammon, monopoly, poker, bridge
 1. the person who likes ivory is the person playing bridge##1
 2. the person who likes lavender is on the far right##1
 3. the game-smoker is on the far right##1
 4. the person playing poker is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
 5. the person who likes grey is on the right of the aristoff-smoker##1
 6. the aristoff-smoker is on the left of the davidoff-smoker##1
 7. the davidoff-smoker is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
 8. the person who likes lavender is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
 9. the person who likes grey is on the left of the person playing bridge##1
10. the person who likes lavender is the person who's hobby is sudoku##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3      |       4        |
| Color      | amber | grey       | ivory        | lavender        |
| Hobby           | singing   | collecting | woodworking   | sudoku |
| Cigar   | aristoff     | davidoff    | oliveros | game        |
| Game           | poker         | backgammon  | bridge       | monopoly         |

