.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-4::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, soy-milk, fanta, milk
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: poppy, daffodil, dahlia, tulip
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skateboarding, cricket, surfing, rugby
There 4 different types of food: grapefruit, pineapple, blueberry, eggplant
1. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
2. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person eating eggplant##1
3. the person who growspoppy is on the far right##1
4. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person eating grapefruit##1
5. the person who growspoppy is on the right of the person who growsdaffodil##1
6. the person who growstulip is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
7. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
8. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the far right##1
9. the person eating blueberry is the person who's sport is rugby##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3     |      4      |
| Beverage           | soy-milk   | lemonade  | milk | fanta |
| Flower   | dahlia | tulip       | daffodil       | poppy     |
| Sport   | surfing       | rugby    | cricket     | skateboarding  |
| Food           | pineapple     | blueberry | eggplant     | grapefruit         |

