.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-5::.
4 different pets are kept: bird, snake, pony, guinea-pig
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: february, april, december, september
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: dahlia, daisy, poppy, azalea
There are 4 different favourite colors: grey, coral, pink, blood-red
1. the person who's birthday is in december is on the far left##1
2. the person who likes grey is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
3. the person who likes coral is on the far left##1
4. the person who growsdaisy is on the left of the person who growsdahlia##1
5. the person who growsazalea is on the right of the person who likes blood-red##1
6. the person who likes blood-red is the person who growspoppy##1
7. the person who growsdahlia is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
8. the owner of the snake is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
9. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the owner of the pony##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |       3       |      4       |
| Pet           | bird  | pony    | snake | guinea-pig |
| Birthday   | december      | april    | february         | september    |
| Flower   | daisy   | dahlia     | poppy          | azalea      |
| Color         | coral | grey | blood-red      | pink      |

