.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-6::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: november, january, april, february
4 different games are played: chess, backgammon, monopoly, bridge
City: san-francisco, paris, nizza, venice
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, water, mirinda, tea
 1. the person who's birthday is in april is the person traveling to san-francisco##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in november is the person traveling to paris##1
 3. the person playing chess is the person traveling to san-francisco##1
 4. the person drinking mirinda is the person who's birthday is in november##1
 5. the person traveling to nizza is the person playing bridge##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
 7. the person playing monopoly is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
 8. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the right of the person traveling to nizza##1
 9. the person playing monopoly is on the far left##1
10. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |     3      |     4     |
| Birthday          | november  | february | april     | january |
| Game           | monopoly  | bridge      | chess | backgammon    |
| City   | paris | nizza  | san-francisco    | venice  |
| Beverage           | mirinda   | tea       | 7up       | water      |

