.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-7::.
4 different games are played: billiard, monopoly, snooker, scrabble
House: art-deco, modern, ranch-style, townhouse
There are 4 different favourite colors: yellow, apricot, blood-red, ivory
There 4 different types of food: avocado, cherry, potato, garlic
 1. the person who likes yellow is the modern house##1
 2. the person eating garlic is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
 3. the person playing snooker is on the right of the ranch-style house##1
 4. the person who likes apricot is on the left of the ranch-style house##1
 5. the modern house is on the right of the person who likes ivory##1
 6. the ranch-style house is on the left of the townhouse house##1
 7. the person who likes yellow is the person eating potato##1
 8. the person playing billiard is on the far left##1
 9. the person playing billiard is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
10. the person eating avocado is on the left of the person eating potato##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Game    | billiard | monopoly     | snooker    | scrabble |
| House       | art-deco | ranch-style    | townhouse | modern |
| Color         | apricot   | blood-red  | ivory        | yellow    |
| Food   | garlic   | cherry | avocado    | potato |

