3. the ritmeester-smoker is on the left of the aristoff-smoker##1
4. the person eating pepper is on the left of the person traveling to colone##1
5. the cain-smoker is on the left of the person who likes black##1
6. the ritmeester-smoker is on the right of the person traveling to nizza##1
7. the person eating artichoke is the person traveling to nizza##1
8. the person traveling to miami is the person who likes black##1
9. the person traveling to venice is the person who likes amber##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |      3      |     4      |
| Color      | coral      | black         | green        | amber      |
| Food           | artichoke | pepper | lemon  | pomegranate  |
| Cigar   | cain    | ritmeester     | aristoff | dannemann     |
| City     | nizza        | miami     | colone     | venice |

