.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-9::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: october, december, september, january
There 4 different types of food: lemon, kiwi, plum, carrot
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: western, spy, disaster, action
City: colone, miami, edinburgh, boston
1. the person watching action movies is on the far left##1
2. the person traveling to miami is on the right of the person watching spy movies##1
3. the person eating kiwi is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
4. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
5. the person traveling to miami is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1
6. the person traveling to boston is the person who's birthday is in january##1
7. the person traveling to edinburgh is the person watching western movies##1
8. the person eating plum is on the far left##1
9. the person eating carrot is the person who's birthday is in january##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |      3      |     4      |
| Birthday         | december | january | september | october     |
| Food   | plum   | carrot       | lemon       | kiwi  |
| Movie-Genre           | action    | spy    | disaster       | western       |
| City     | colone     | boston        | miami   | edinburgh |

