3. the person driving the ship is on the far left##1
4. the person driving the bus is the ritmeester-smoker##1
5. the person driving the bike is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1
6. the bongani-smoker is on the left of the person who likes red##1
7. the owner of the goat is on the right of the prince-smoker##1
8. the bongani-smoker is the person driving the bike##1
9. the owner of the snake is on the right of the person who likes turquise##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |    3     |      4      |
| Transport      | ship     | bike           | trike    | bus    |
| Cigar         | old-henry  | bongani | prince  | ritmeester |
| Pet   | rat     | snake     | hamster | goat   |
| Color         | turquise | green     | red | aquamarine     |

