 7. the dannemann-smoker is on the left of the person driving the ship##1
 8. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
 9. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
10. the accountant is the vegafina-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |      3       |     4     |
